{"name":"Italian Angels for Growth","permalink":"italian-angels-for-growth","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/financial-organization/italian-angels-for-growth","homepage_url":"http://www.italianangels.net","blog_url":"","blog_feed_url":"","twitter_username":"italianangels","phone_number":"","description":"Angel Group","email_address":"info@italianangels.net","number_of_employees":null,"founded_year":2007,"founded_month":null,"founded_day":null,"tag_list":"business-angels, angel-investors, angel-group, italy","alias_list":"","created_at":"Mon Oct 25 20:47:04 UTC 2010","updated_at":"Fri Oct 19 21:35:49 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Italian Angels for Growth (IAG) is the largest angel group in Italy and is promoted and managed exclusively by individual investors.\nIAG was established in 2007 by nine co-founders and now comprises of more than 100 carefully selected angel investors characterized by their passion for entrepreneurship and early stage financing.\nIAG facilitates early stage investments for its members. The group looks at potential investments in any sector where there is at least one expert member. IAG seeks investment opportunities from €300.000 to €800.000 mainly for early stage businesses based in Italy and is open to cross border investments, thanks to the nature of the group and to the high international experience and exposure of most of its members. </p>\n\n<p>IAG members have closed thirteen deals for a total invested amount in excess of €6M. IAG members committed capital in potential deals un to a  the sum  in excess of €20M. \nIAG is a proud and active member of the European Business Angels Network (EBAN) and the Italian Venture Capital Hub. IAG is also a strong contributor to initiatives such as Partnership for Growth. At the same time, IAG Directors and members are frequent speakers at education events and in Universities in Italy and abroad. </p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,39],"assets/images/resized/0010/7216/107216v1-max-150x150.p